'''北極圈科學博物館'''（Arktikum Science Museum）是位於[[芬蘭|芬蘭]][[羅瓦涅米|羅瓦涅米]]的一座[[博物館|博物館]]和科學中心。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.visitfinland.com/services/service/arktikum/|title = Arktikum Arctic Museum and Science Centre|accessdate = 2016-02-28|author = |date = |publisher = Visit Finland|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304010625/http://www.visitfinland.com/services/service/arktikum/|dead-url = no}}</ref>北極圈科學博物館也是一個旅遊景點，並且也用來舉辦會議，還有咖啡廳和圖書館服務。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.arktikum.fi/EN/services.html|title = SERVICES|accessdate = 2016-02-28|author = |date = |publisher = Arktikum Museum and Arctic Science Centre|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305054317/http://www.arktikum.fi/EN/services.html|archivedate = 2016-03-05}}</ref>北極圈科學博物館內部分為北極中心和拉普蘭省博物館兩個部分。北極圈科學博物館在1992年12月6日開始對公眾開放。<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.ulapland.fi/InEnglish/About-us/Visit-Us/University-Buildings|title = Premises|accessdate = 2016-02-28|author = |date = |publisher = University of Lapland|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160225160446/http://www.ulapland.fi/InEnglish/About-us/Visit-Us/University-Buildings|archive-date = 2016-02-25|dead-url = yes}}</ref>

